targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  window_start,
  sum(col_1) as total_logs
FROM ngx_statistics
WHERE $__timeFilter(window_start)
GROUP BY window_start
ORDER BY window_start

SELECT
  agent,
  ua_platform,
  count(*) as count,
FROM ngx_access_log
WHERE $__timeFilter(access_time)
GROUP BY agent, ua_platform
ORDER BY count desc
LIMIT 100

panels.description: Number of requests per streaming format

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  status::string,
  sum(col_1) as count
FROM ngx_statistics
WHERE $__timeFilter(window_start)
GROUP BY status
ORDER BY count desc
LIMIT 100

panels.title: Status Code

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  referer,
  count(*) as count,
FROM ngx_access_log
WHERE $__timeFilter(access_time)
GROUP BY referer
ORDER BY count desc
LIMIT 100

SELECT
  request, ua_platform, referer, client, access_time, status, size, agent
FROM ngx_access_log
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(access_time)
  AND matches(request, '$requestLike')
ORDER BY access_time
LIMIT 50

panels.description: Number of requests per streaming format

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  ${treeMapGroupBy} as item,
  count(*) as count,
  count(security_rules LIKE '${secRulesLike}' or NULL) / count (*) as PercentError
FROM ${ds2}
WHERE $__timeFilter(req_time_sec)
GROUP BY item
ORDER BY count desc
LIMIT ${treemapCells}

panels.title: Security Rate for top ${treemapCells} ${treeMapGroupBy} (Excludes error rates below ${minErrorRate})

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  security_rules,
  count(*) as count,
FROM ${ds2}
WHERE $__timeFilter(req_time_sec)
GROUP BY security_rules
ORDER BY count desc
LIMIT ${treemapCells}
